data.description: Step into this charming cottage-style home in Sabine Pass and experience a cozy retreat that's perfect for families. This 4 bed/2 bath home boasts a spacious front porch, perfect for enjoying the lovely Texas weather. The breakfast area is perfect for casual dining, and the ample parking and concrete driveway make it easy to entertain guests. The home also offers a large concrete area under the house, ideal for gatherings and outdoor activities. Plus, the location near refinery expansions and in the highly desirable Sabine Pass ISD makes this home an opportunity not to be missed.New windstorm certified roof & Morgan building to stay with home. Seller is willing to purchase Home Warranty for the first year.
